1
00:01:03,480 --> 00:01:06,340
Preliminary findings suggest death by poisoning.

2
00:01:11,080 --> 00:01:12,140
It's this arsenic.

3
00:01:12,720 --> 00:01:13,440
Rat poison.

4
00:01:19,039 --> 00:01:21,000
The victim had just eaten and drunk alcohol.

5
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:22,930
But there are no leftovers around,

6
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:24,800
which means someone cleared them away.

7
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:25,520
Poisoning.

8
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:27,539
Someone murdered him.

9
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:33,440
Why does this man look so familiar?

10
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:42,660
This is Zheng Jinxian.

11
00:01:47,479 --> 00:01:49,210
Didn't he go on a business trip?

12
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:52,090
Is he Zheng Jinxian?

13
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,250
Why did you kill him?

14
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,050
It was Ma Yanmei.

15
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:57,720
The Zheng family's concubine sent me here.

16
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:59,380
Ma Yanmei told you to kill him?

17
00:01:59,960 --> 00:02:01,160
No, no, no. No.

18
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:03,290
I'll tell you the truth.

19
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:04,780
That Ma Yanmei,

20
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,980
she was lonely, so she seduced me.

21
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:10,240
If you have good stuff in the future,

22
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:11,460
no matter how late,

23
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,280
come find me.

24
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:20,130
She asked me to meet her at 8 p.m.

25
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,720
at the General's Temple for a tryst.

26
00:02:21,720 --> 00:02:23,040
She hit on you?

27
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:25,000
With your looks?

28
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:26,760
I'm telling the truth.

29
00:02:26,760 --> 00:02:27,960
We knew each other.

30
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:31,530
Xiaomei.

31
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:32,380
Going home?

32
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,079
It's getting dark.

33
00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:36,450
Let me walk you home.

34
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,490
Get out of my way.

35
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:38,420
Look at you.

36
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:40,000
You're just a widow.

37
00:02:40,079 --> 00:02:42,560
If you get into trouble, no one will look after you.

38
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:43,420
How about this?

39
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:44,970
Invite me in for a cup of tea,

40
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,960
and I'll look out for you.

41
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:49,520
Get out of my way.

42
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:51,250
If you don't move, I'll scream.

43
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:52,810
Go ahead and scream.

44
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:54,880
Let everyone come and see.

45
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:56,440
A widow is having an affair.

46
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:57,280
I'd like to see...

47
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:59,000
who's the one losing face.

48
00:03:00,200 --> 00:03:01,360
Let go of me.

49
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:03,240
Help!

50
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:07,160
Help!

51
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:10,000
Let go of me.

52
00:03:10,600 --> 00:03:11,600
You smell so good.

53
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:15,440
Come any closer,

54
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:17,100
and I'll take you down with me.

55
00:03:18,079 --> 00:03:18,480
Fine.

56
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:19,400
Fine.

57
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:21,570
I'll let you off the hook today.

58
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:23,400
Go home, wash up, and wait for me.

59
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:23,960
Get lost.

60
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:25,320
Get lost!

61
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:27,079
So, you and Ma Yanmei

62
00:03:27,200 --> 00:03:28,320
conspired to kill Zheng Jinxian,

63
00:03:28,320 --> 00:03:28,980
didn't you?

64
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:29,960
No, no, no.

65
00:03:30,079 --> 00:03:31,120
Officer, please.

66
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:32,920
I really just came for a secret tryst.

67
00:03:32,920 --> 00:03:34,120
I didn't kill anyone.

68
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:36,360
I don't even know who this dead guy is.

69
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,490
You're still lying.

70
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:39,040
I'm telling the truth.

71
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:39,680
Lies.

72
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:41,610
Didi, come look at this.

73
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:48,960
This guy.

74
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,320
Gu Mancang.

75
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:53,130
He isn't Zheng Jinxian.

76
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:55,090
He's the one who called the car.

77
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:57,450
They look so much alike.

78
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:58,720
No wonder we mixed the two up

79
00:03:58,720 --> 00:04:00,400
based on the sketch alone.

80
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:05,340
Gu Mancang impersonated Zheng Jinxian.

81
00:04:05,920 --> 00:04:08,780
He shaved and disguised himself sitting in the car,

82
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,730
trying to assume his identity.

83
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:13,800
Sir, let's go.

84
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:14,800
Just listen to me.

85
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,480
You've got the wrong guy.

86
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:18,079
I'm not a suspect.

87
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:19,760
Officer, he's innocent.

88
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:20,560
You can't do this to him.

89
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,440
Yes, Sir.

90
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:23,840
Innocent? Wrongly accused?

91
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:26,040
Would I frame a good man?

92
00:04:26,520 --> 00:04:27,920
I really didn't kill anyone.

93
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:28,560
Tell me.

94
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:30,520
Would I arrest you if you were good?

95
00:04:30,520 --> 00:04:30,840
I definitely...

96
00:04:30,840 --> 00:04:32,680
Our Chief personally ordered

97
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:33,280
the arrest of

98
00:04:33,280 --> 00:04:35,520
the serial murder suspect.

99
00:04:36,520 --> 00:04:36,960
Move.

100
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:38,400
No!

101
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,000
Honey.

102
00:04:39,159 --> 00:04:40,320
Are you okay? Honey, go.

103
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:41,040
- Honey.
- Dali.

104
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:41,400
Move it.

105
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:43,440
You're obstructing justice.

106
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:46,440
Don't try to fake an injury.

107
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:47,080
Honey.

108
00:04:47,080 --> 00:04:48,240
Take him away.

109
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,440
Officer, please. Dali.

110
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:50,600
My wife is pregnant.

111
00:04:50,840 --> 00:04:52,240
You've got the wrong guy.

112
00:04:55,440 --> 00:04:56,159
All right.

113
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,120
Chief,

114
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:02,280
why was Man Dali arrested again?

115
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:04,400
Didn't he clear his name last time?

116
00:05:04,400 --> 00:05:05,860
As soon as he was released,

117
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,100
someone else died.

118
00:05:07,440 --> 00:05:08,170
It looks like

119
00:05:08,280 --> 00:05:09,840
he is the serial killer.

120
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:10,520
Chief,

121
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,520
there are many suspicious points in this case.

122
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:14,200
I don't think Man Dali is the murderer.

123
00:05:14,200 --> 00:05:16,200
The higher-ups want me to close the case by tomorrow.

124
00:05:16,200 --> 00:05:17,320
Who else could it be

125
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:18,940
but that rickshaw puller?

126
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:20,840
Lowlifes like him will do anything

127
00:05:20,840 --> 00:05:22,320
for a little money.

128
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:24,280
Man Dali just confessed.

129
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:25,680
He said he killed them all.

130
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:26,360
What?

131
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:31,240
I have an important clue to tell you.

132
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,760
Ma Yanmei had a husband

133
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,960
who died in Zheng Jinxian's factory.

134
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:36,560
Talk later. I'm busy right now.

135
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:37,890
Another person is dead.

136
00:05:38,159 --> 00:05:39,220
Gu Mancang, right?

137
00:05:40,159 --> 00:05:41,680
I mean the real Gu Mancang.

138
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:43,600
The one who died before was Zheng Jinxian.

139
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:44,460
How do you know?

140
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:47,920
Gu Mancang's body was found at the General Temple.

141
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:51,159
I asked the old neighbors near the Zheng house.

142
00:05:51,159 --> 00:05:51,840
They said

143
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:55,180
Zheng Jinxian rarely went out after getting vitiligo.

144
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:58,200
So Gu Mancang managed the Zheng household.

145
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:00,000
The servants who came later

146
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:02,040
always thought he was Zheng Jinxian.

147
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:03,760
So according to our theory,

148
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:07,060
Gu Mancang successfully assumed his identity.

149
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:08,640
Then who killed him?

150
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:10,960
I suspect Ma Yanmei.

151
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:14,040
Because she held a grudge

152
00:06:14,400 --> 00:06:15,720
against both Gu Mancang and Zheng Jinxian.

153
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:17,320
I've sent people to watch the Zheng house.

154
00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:18,120
She can't run.

155
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:19,720
The important thing is,

156
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:21,520
Man Dali has been taken back to the police station,

157
00:06:21,520 --> 00:06:23,440
and he has confessed.

158
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:24,400
What?

159
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:30,210
Come out.

160
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,300
What are you doing?

161
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,000
Why plead guilty?

162
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:34,240
It clearly wasn't you.

163
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:35,320
Why are you doing this?

164
00:06:35,320 --> 00:06:35,920
It was me.

165
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,280
I killed them.

166
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:38,680
I... I killed them.

167
00:06:39,159 --> 00:06:39,680
Dali.

168
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:41,360
We've found clues.

169
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:43,920
Zheng Jinxian's death has nothing to do with you.

170
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:45,980
And neither does the butler's death.

171
00:06:46,200 --> 00:06:48,330
Someone forced you to say this, right?

172
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:50,159
Who? Who forced you?

173
00:06:50,159 --> 00:06:51,000
No, no.

174
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,530
No one forced me.

175
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:54,250
I killed Zheng Jinxian.

176
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:56,400
I... I killed Gu Mancang.

177
00:06:56,760 --> 00:06:57,400
It was me.

178
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:59,520
Dali, don't be stupid.

179
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:01,420
Pleading guilty means death.

180
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:03,040
Don't you care about Juan?

181
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:03,880
Do you want your child

182
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:05,160
to be born without a father?

183
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:05,640
No.

184
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:08,100
I was after Master Zheng's money,

185
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:10,480
so I killed him with opium.

186
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,360
After Gu Mancang found out,

187
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:12,890
I just...

188
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,320
I silenced him.

189
00:07:14,960 --> 00:07:15,820
It... it was me.

190
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:17,200
I... I did it all.

191
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:18,690
I... I plead guilty.

192
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:20,040
I, Man Dali, must plead guilty.

193
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:20,960
Nonsense.

194
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,120
I plead guilty.

195
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:22,880
Get out here.

196
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:23,960
Come out. I must plead guilty.

197
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:24,800
Go home.

198
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:25,360
No.

199
00:07:25,400 --> 00:07:27,200
It clearly wasn't you. I'm not going out.

200
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:27,840
I plead guilty.

201
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:28,160
Come out.

202
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:28,800
I'm not going out.

203
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:30,320
Let's step outside and talk.

204
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:30,800
I must confess.

205
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:31,930
Come out, Yao Zhidi.

206
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:34,480
Who allowed you to release the prisoner?

207
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:35,610
He is not a criminal.

208
00:07:35,840 --> 00:07:36,800
He was framed.

209
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:39,680
It's not up to you whether he's innocent or not.

210
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,840
Man Dali has already confessed.

211
00:07:40,840 --> 00:07:42,100
The case is closed now.

212
00:07:42,520 --> 00:07:43,050
Captain,

213
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:44,400
we found out something.

214
00:07:44,400 --> 00:07:46,200
It was Zheng Jinxian's butler, Gu Mancang,

215
00:07:46,200 --> 00:07:47,440
who called the rickshaw

216
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:49,000
and put the body on it.

217
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:51,420
Gu Mancang is likely the real killer.

218
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:53,520
The higher-ups

219
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:56,159
expect me to close the case by tomorrow.

220
00:07:56,159 --> 00:07:57,200
If he doesn't confess,

221
00:07:57,200 --> 00:07:58,659
this case can't be closed.

222
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:00,840
Wang Shui,

223
00:08:02,320 --> 00:08:03,450
as a police officer,

224
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:05,400
is this how you trifle with human life?

225
00:08:05,400 --> 00:08:06,730
It's all because of you.

226
00:08:07,280 --> 00:08:07,800
Chief,

227
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:09,520
give me a little more time

228
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:10,720
to get to the bottom of this case.

229
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:12,160
Drop it.

230
00:08:12,840 --> 00:08:15,100
Tell Yao Zhidi to wrap things up quickly.

231
00:08:15,760 --> 00:08:17,360
It's Yao Zhidi's first case.

232
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:18,400
She doesn't have much experience.

233
00:08:18,400 --> 00:08:18,920
I think

234
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:20,840
she must have missed something.

235
00:08:20,840 --> 00:08:22,600
Help her close the case immediately.

236
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:24,640
I want to do her uncle a favor.

237
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:25,600
Remember,

238
00:08:25,760 --> 00:08:27,320
keep a low profile.

239
00:08:27,400 --> 00:08:28,130
Understood?

240
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:29,810
Chief, alright.

241
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:30,160
I...

242
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,240
I'll send someone to handle it.

243
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:33,039
You go do whatever you need to do.

244
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:36,059
As for me, I have to go play cards with the Vice Mayor.

245
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,720
You were the one who wanted to investigate.

246
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:44,049
You promised the Chief.

247
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:46,600
Now, just so the Chief can do your uncle a favor,

248
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:48,460
he's making me clean up your mess.

249
00:08:53,040 --> 00:08:55,320
Isn't investigating about finding the truth?

250
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:56,920
Never wronging an innocent person,

251
00:08:56,920 --> 00:08:58,580
and never letting a bad guy go.

252
00:08:58,880 --> 00:09:00,440
If we let Man Dali take the fall,

253
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:01,720
then the real killer

254
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:03,360
gets to walk free?

255
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:05,080
You little girl.

256
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:08,140
What does police work have to do with you?

257
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:12,240
It certainly has something to do with me as a forensic examiner.

258
00:09:12,240 --> 00:09:14,640
Police investigations require evidence.

259
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:18,160
Looks like we're working late tonight.

260
00:09:19,280 --> 00:09:20,540
For true human rights.

261
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:33,360
Leucoderma.

262
00:09:34,680 --> 00:09:35,810
He has vitiligo too.

263
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:40,770
Brachydactyly.

264
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:43,640
Dominant inheritance.

265
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:48,730
Dominant inheritance.

266
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:54,260
They are related by blood.

267
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:57,680
It is a fact that the person has been dead for two days.

268
00:09:57,680 --> 00:09:59,520
Gu Mancang and Zheng Jinxian are related by blood.

269
00:09:59,520 --> 00:10:00,580
That is also a fact.

270
00:10:00,880 --> 00:10:03,010
There is definitely more to this case.

271
00:10:08,560 --> 00:10:10,290
Do you really think I'm stupid?

272
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:12,040
Don't you think I can see

273
00:10:12,040 --> 00:10:13,500
that Man Dali is innocent?

274
00:10:15,400 --> 00:10:17,520
You all know about the secret torture methods

275
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:18,720
we use in our bureau.

276
00:10:20,800 --> 00:10:21,920
And you should know

277
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:24,960
that Man Dali has been fired from the rickshaw company.

278
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:26,220
Even if he gets out now,

279
00:10:27,040 --> 00:10:28,170
he'll be penniless.

280
00:10:29,280 --> 00:10:30,680
His wife is having a difficult labor

281
00:10:30,680 --> 00:10:33,010
and needs money urgently at the hospital.

282
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:35,000
He only confessed because

283
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:37,200
the Chief promised him those 500 silver dollars.

284
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,330
That's why he did it.

285
00:10:40,760 --> 00:10:41,520
A human life.

286
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:43,040
A human life.

287
00:10:43,640 --> 00:10:44,970
Worth only 500 dollars.

288
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:50,060
I blame myself for being useless.

289
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,360
My wife, Juanzi,

290
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:54,880
has suffered her whole life with a lousy rickshaw puller like me.

291
00:10:54,880 --> 00:10:56,240
.

292
00:10:58,520 --> 00:11:00,720
My worthless life is not worth pitying.

293
00:11:01,560 --> 00:11:02,720
I have to make sure...

294
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:04,640
make sure my wife and child

295
00:11:04,800 --> 00:11:05,960
live a good life.

296
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:14,930
It's delicious.

297
00:11:22,800 --> 00:11:23,460
Delicious.

298
00:11:36,600 --> 00:11:37,330
Officer Yao,

299
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:39,000
Wuyue,

300
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:41,170
I know you're both good people.

301
00:11:42,280 --> 00:11:44,210
For everything you've done for me,

302
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:45,760
for your great kindness,

303
00:11:45,760 --> 00:11:46,480
in my next life,

304
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:48,610
I'll do whatever it takes to repay you.

305
00:11:48,880 --> 00:11:49,810
But in this life,

306
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:52,400
I... I just want my wife...

307
00:11:52,560 --> 00:11:54,690
I want to live a good life with my child.

308
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:56,280
Regarding this case,

309
00:11:56,640 --> 00:11:58,170
let's stop investigating.

310
00:11:59,200 --> 00:11:59,720
Okay?

311
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:08,560
I beg you.

312
00:12:09,280 --> 00:12:10,720
Let's stop.

313
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:16,560
Let's stop.

314
00:12:19,560 --> 00:12:21,800
I'm begging you.

315
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:37,940
To figure everything out,

316
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:39,530
we must go back to the start.

317
00:12:40,920 --> 00:12:43,250
To solve the White Hair Blood Corpse Case,

318
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:45,320
we must find out how the body was moved.

319
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:46,840
That Gu Mancang killed Zheng Jinxian

320
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:47,900
is just our theory.

321
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:49,640
Now, shouldn't Gu Mancang's death

322
00:12:49,640 --> 00:12:51,570
be the focus of the investigation?

323
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:53,500
I heard from a servant.

324
00:12:53,920 --> 00:12:55,120
Two days ago, the Madam

325
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:57,720
had us move a large box to the General's Temple.

326
00:12:58,080 --> 00:13:00,010
It was supposed to hold saltpeter,

327
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:02,800
but later it held Zheng Jinxian's body.

328
00:13:03,040 --> 00:13:03,560
And

329
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:06,380
it was Ma Yanmei who ordered it moved.

330
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:09,120
Ma Yanmei and Gu Mancang

331
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:11,080
conspired to kill Zheng Jinxian.

332
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:11,960
Then Gu Mancang's death

333
00:13:11,960 --> 00:13:13,690
must be connected to Ma Yanmei.

334
00:13:15,560 --> 00:13:17,220
We need to find that box first.

335
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:18,930
Then I'll make Ma Yanmei

336
00:13:19,040 --> 00:13:20,170
confess her motive.

337
00:13:20,640 --> 00:13:21,900
Will that really work?

338
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:25,120
Zheng Jinxian's death had nothing to do with Man Dali anyway.

339
00:13:25,120 --> 00:13:27,450
If Ma Yanmei admits to killing Gu Mancang,

340
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:29,140
then the case is truly solved.

341
00:13:29,400 --> 00:13:30,860
Don't you agree, Captain?

342
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:32,650
Captain,

343
00:13:32,920 --> 00:13:34,920
give us one more day to investigate.

344
00:13:34,920 --> 00:13:35,450
I believe

345
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:37,360
you want fairness and justice too.

346
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:37,760
Right?

347
00:13:38,640 --> 00:13:39,240
Half a day.

348
00:13:40,040 --> 00:13:42,300
And don't let anyone at the station know.

349
00:13:43,520 --> 00:13:44,720
By tomorrow morning,

350
00:13:45,720 --> 00:13:47,440
you're off this case.

351
00:13:49,800 --> 00:13:50,160
Okay.

352
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:56,200
Everything you said is true.

353
00:13:57,640 --> 00:13:58,240
Miss Qiu,

354
00:13:58,640 --> 00:13:59,680
even if you don't believe me,

355
00:13:59,680 --> 00:14:01,340
you surely trust Officer Yao.

356
00:14:01,480 --> 00:14:02,840
Otherwise, she wouldn't have let you come here.

357
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:04,960
I can't believe Chief Song

358
00:14:05,160 --> 00:14:07,420
found a scapegoat just to close the case.

359
00:14:07,840 --> 00:14:08,440
It seems

360
00:14:08,920 --> 00:14:10,960
he wants to quell the unrest

361
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:12,840
and control public opinion.

362
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:13,840
What should we do?

363
00:14:14,040 --> 00:14:15,760
Should I go to Mr. Luo

364
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:17,260
for legal assistance?

365
00:14:18,480 --> 00:14:20,280
Since he wants to quell the unrest,

366
00:14:20,280 --> 00:14:22,000
we need to stir up public opinion.

367
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:23,260
Let the whole city know

368
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:24,720
that Man Dali was framed.

369
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:25,600
Okay.

370
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:28,240
I'll tell the family and our brothers at the company

371
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:29,920
to protest outside the police station.

372
00:14:29,920 --> 00:14:32,250
We also need to coordinate with Yao Zhidi.

373
00:14:33,280 --> 00:14:34,080
These are...

374
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:35,530
Why are you here?

375
00:14:36,760 --> 00:14:39,280
Wang Shui said we can't investigate at the station.

376
00:14:39,280 --> 00:14:40,520
Moli said you were here,

377
00:14:40,520 --> 00:14:41,380
so we came over.

378
00:14:41,680 --> 00:14:42,800
Feel free to use this place.

379
00:14:42,800 --> 00:14:44,200
Make yourselves at home.

380
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:45,080
Dr. Yang,

381
00:14:45,560 --> 00:14:47,290
does this board look familiar?

382
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:49,880
How can you be sure it's these pieces of rotten wood?

383
00:14:49,880 --> 00:14:51,920
When you pressed me onto the box,

384
00:14:52,520 --> 00:14:53,980
I smelled a scent of death.

385
00:14:54,520 --> 00:14:56,560
The smell on Zheng Jinxian's clothes

386
00:14:56,560 --> 00:14:57,760
was exactly the same.

387
00:15:03,760 --> 00:15:05,520
I remember seeing similar wood chips

388
00:15:05,520 --> 00:15:07,120
on Zheng Jinxian's clothes.

389
00:15:07,280 --> 00:15:08,680
It was damp-proofed fir.

390
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:12,320
We suspect Zheng Jinxian's body

391
00:15:12,320 --> 00:15:14,720
was moved to the General Temple using this.

392
00:15:15,320 --> 00:15:17,120
Gu Mancang moved the body.

393
00:15:17,920 --> 00:15:19,920
Ma Yanmei created the smoke screen.

394
00:15:20,920 --> 00:15:21,920
But how do we prove

395
00:15:21,960 --> 00:15:24,080
the box was originally at the Zheng Residence?

396
00:15:24,080 --> 00:15:26,140
The Zheng family won't admit to that.

397
00:15:26,240 --> 00:15:27,680
Renzin Chamber of Commerce

398
00:15:27,680 --> 00:15:29,080
is Ji Wenxuan's company.

399
00:15:29,320 --> 00:15:31,720
If this originally held saltpeter,

400
00:15:32,360 --> 00:15:34,560
then only Renzin Chamber of Commerce's shipping

401
00:15:34,560 --> 00:15:35,800
could safely transport these boxes

402
00:15:35,800 --> 00:15:37,480
to the Zheng Match Factory.

403
00:15:37,920 --> 00:15:39,080
In other words,

404
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:42,880
Ji Wenxuan can prove the transportation of the box.

405
00:15:43,720 --> 00:15:46,980
If we can prove that this box came from the Zheng residence,

406
00:15:47,520 --> 00:15:49,380
let's see how Ma Yanmei denies it.

407
00:15:49,560 --> 00:15:51,080
I'll contact the Renjin Chamber of Commerce

408
00:15:51,080 --> 00:15:53,280
and ask Brother Wenxuan for the list of porters.

409
00:15:53,280 --> 00:15:55,360
There are at least several hundred porters

410
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:56,960
and laborers in the Renjin Chamber of Commerce.

411
00:15:56,960 --> 00:15:58,240
If we ask them one by one,

412
00:15:58,240 --> 00:15:59,560
we won't finish until the day after tomorrow.

413
00:15:59,560 --> 00:16:01,290
How do you know if you don't try?

414
00:16:01,360 --> 00:16:02,280
We just need to ask the porters

415
00:16:02,280 --> 00:16:04,940
who took orders on Furong Street three days ago,

416
00:16:04,960 --> 00:16:06,520
and we can narrow down the scope.

417
00:16:06,520 --> 00:16:07,480
The box.

418
00:16:10,040 --> 00:16:11,320
I have a faster way.
